DESCRIPTION:• Chanu presenting\n• *how to measure interfacial tension???*\n
   • droplet method of Nakamoto didn't seem to work.  Reline droplet\n    f
 ell through water and water droplet spread onto reline.\n• Chanu to get be
 tter Schlieren.\n• Chanu try NMR of top and bottom phases (water\, reline)
  with time to\n  confirm ChCl:urea stoichiometry.\n• Esam will re-measure 
 second virial coefficients.  Shift paper focus\n  to Gly:GdmCl DES\, since
  that has better Zimm plot.
